            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Israelites%20had%20been%20granted%20the%20victory%2C%20it%20still%20took%20them%20a%20long%20time%20to%20subdue%20their%20enemies.%20%22Little%20by%20little%22%20and%20%22inch%20by%20inch%22%20is%20the%20pattern%20for%20gaining%20the%20territory%20promised%20to%20you.%20Sometimes%20your%20progress%20may%20be%20very%20slow%2C%20but%20you%20must%20fight%20on%20because%20every%20enemy%20you%20leave%20in%20your%20territory%20will%20become%20%22a%20pain%20in%20your%20side%20and%20a%20thorn%20in%20your%20eyes%22%20(Joshua%2023%3A13).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EChrist%20Himself%20is%20now%20seated%20at%20the%20right%20hand%20of%20God%20until%20He%20makes%20your%20enemies%20a%20footstool%20for%20your%20feet%20(Luke%2020%3A43).%20Though%20the%20battle%20may%20be%20long%2C%20you%20are%20assured%20a%20victory%20in%20the%20end%3A%20%22Each%20one%20of%20you%20will%20put%20to%20flight%20a%20thousand%20of%20the%20enemy%2C%20for%20the%20Lord%20your%20God%20fights%20for%20you%2C%20just%20as%20he%20has%20promised%22%20(Joshua%2023%3A10).%20Fight%20on%20until%20every%20promise%20from%20God%20comes%20true%2C%20for%20surely%20the%20enemy%20who%20contests%20you%20is%20trying%20to%20resist%20the%20Word%20of%20God.%20The%20promise%20in%20Psalm%2089%3A23%20is%20clear%3A%20%22I%20will%20beat%20down%20his%20adversaries%20before%20him%20and%20destroy%20those%20who%20hate%20him.%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20long%20battle%2C%20remember%20that%20your%20character%20is%20being%20transformed.%20%22Count%20it%20all%20joy%22%20.%20.%20.%20your%20patience%20is%20growing%20(James%201%3A2%20KJV)!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
