            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Joshua.22:21-23:16",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJoshua%2022%3A21-23%3A16%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_21%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20people%20of%20Reuben%2C%20Gad%2C%20and%20the%20half-tribe%20of%20Manasseh%20answered%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20clans%20of%20Israel%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_22%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20Mighty%20One%2C%20is%20God!%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20Mighty%20One%2C%20is%20God!%20He%20knows%20the%20truth%2C%20and%20may%20Israel%20know%20it%2C%20too!%20We%20have%20not%20built%20the%20altar%20in%20treacherous%20rebellion%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20If%20we%20have%20done%20so%2C%20do%20not%20spare%20our%20lives%20this%20day.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_23%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20we%20have%20built%20an%20altar%20for%20ourselves%20to%20turn%20away%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20to%20offer%20burnt%20offerings%20or%20grain%20offerings%20or%20peace%20offerings%2C%20may%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20himself%20punish%20us.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_24%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20truth%20is%2C%20we%20have%20built%20this%20altar%20because%20we%20fear%20that%20in%20the%20future%20your%20descendants%20will%20say%20to%20ours%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWhat%20right%20do%20you%20have%20to%20worship%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_25%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20placed%20the%20Jordan%20River%20as%20a%20barrier%20between%20our%20people%20and%20you%20people%20of%20Reuben%20and%20Gad.%20You%20have%20no%20claim%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x2019%3B%20So%20your%20descendants%20may%20prevent%20our%20descendants%20from%20worshiping%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_26%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20we%20decided%20to%20build%20the%20altar%2C%20not%20for%20burnt%20offerings%20or%20sacrifices%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_27%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3Ebut%20as%20a%20memorial.%20It%20will%20remind%20our%20descendants%20and%20your%20descendants%20that%20we%2C%20too%2C%20have%20the%20right%20to%20worship%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20at%20his%20sanctuary%20with%20our%20burnt%20offerings%2C%20sacrifices%2C%20and%20peace%20offerings.%20Then%20your%20descendants%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20say%20to%20ours%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20have%20no%20claim%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_28%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIf%20they%20say%20this%2C%20our%20descendants%20can%20reply%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BLook%20at%20this%20copy%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20altar%20that%20our%20ancestors%20made.%20It%20is%20not%20for%20burnt%20offerings%20or%20sacrifices%3B%20it%20is%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20relationship%20both%20of%20us%20have%20with%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_29%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3EFar%20be%20it%20from%20us%20to%20rebel%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20turn%20away%20from%20him%20by%20building%20our%20own%20altar%20for%20burnt%20offerings%2C%20grain%20offerings%2C%20or%20sacrifices.%20Only%20the%20altar%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20that%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Tabernacle%20may%20be%20used%20for%20that%20purpose.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_30%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Phinehas%20the%20priest%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20community%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20heads%20of%20the%20clans%20of%20Israel%26%23x2014%3Bheard%20this%20from%20the%20tribes%20of%20Reuben%2C%20Gad%2C%20and%20the%20half-tribe%20of%20Manasseh%2C%20they%20were%20satisfied.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_31%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EPhinehas%20son%20of%20Eleazar%2C%20the%20priest%2C%20replied%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BToday%20we%20know%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20among%20us%20because%20you%20have%20not%20committed%20this%20treachery%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20as%20we%20thought.%20Instead%2C%20you%20have%20rescued%20Israel%20from%20being%20destroyed%20by%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_32%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Phinehas%20son%20of%20Eleazar%2C%20the%20priest%2C%20and%20the%20other%20leaders%20left%20the%20tribes%20of%20Reuben%20and%20Gad%20in%20Gilead%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20land%20of%20Canaan%20to%20tell%20the%20Israelites%20what%20had%20happened.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_33%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20all%20the%20Israelites%20were%20satisfied%20and%20praised%20God%20and%20spoke%20no%20more%20of%20war%20against%20Reuben%20and%20Gad.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_22_34%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20people%20of%20Reuben%20and%20Gad%20named%20the%20altar%20%26%23x201C%3BWitness%2C%26%23x201D%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E22%3A34%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Some%20manuscripts%20lack%20this%20word.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20they%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%20is%20a%20witness%20between%20us%20and%20them%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20our%20God%2C%20too.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_23_1%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJoshua%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJoshua%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Final%20Words%20to%20Israel%3C%2F